{"tid":312899,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【趣blogblog】30隻最衰港股　一大同通點（股榮）","createTime":"2017-07-08T00:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T04:38:02.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eebe21ffb35841d7005956344f2fa0c20e26c5af","tid":312899,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:22:27.000Z","msg":"今年迄今跌得最慘烈港股，主板是中國集成(1027)瀉95%，創業板是翠如bb股聯旺(8217)瀉98%，兩隻皆是David Webb 50隻黑名單之內。統計頭30隻跌得最PK主板股份，Webb 50隻黑名單中，有11隻上榜，但另一個有趣發現，是30隻重傷股中，竟有22隻近年曾經改名，百分比超過七成。<br />\n<br />\n港股數目約二千間，過去三年改名的上市公司，平均每年都超過120間，而名字完全改變的接近一半，約60間。公司改名主要有兩個原因，一是主業改變要配合，另一個是先前個名臭晒，逼不得已換名，希望蛋散唔記得當作新公司，重新開始過。<br />\n<br />\n上周有間聯合光伏(686)的上市公司改名為熊貓綠能，這間公司近十年已改名五次，平均每兩年一次。08年底前稱為Gay Giano、然後改為太益，2011年則改為金保利，三年後改為聯合光伏，然後今年就改為熊貓綠能。<br />\n<br />\n記得2014年4月寫過一篇《青蛙不會變王子》的文章，曾經講過，若要人不知，唔好太低B，公司改名雖然非常阿Q，但橋唔怕舊，最緊要有人受。大家可以翻閱30隻衰股大表，相信很多散戶已經忘了昔日舊名，當炒風重臨，大家又中過冧把降，能怪誰。<br />\n<br />\n或者，下一次大家聽完冧把後，不妨稍為做下功課，了解這間似熟非熟的公司。方法很簡單，去David Webb網站( <a href=\"https://webb-site.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=8d68d9ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com</a> )首頁，右上角有欄Stock code的物體，打股票代號，就會去到該公司介紹頁面，中間部分有齊這間公司過去中英文名稱變動。<br />\n<br />\n很多散戶埋怨炒股經常輸錢，但捫心自問有否曾做過功課先落注。一次又一次中伏，俾人說是無能，沒錯吧！<br />\n<br />\n股榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstockwing1&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=68e39c11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499436065_8a43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499436065_8a43.jpg&h=f8374919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170707/large/1499436070_1231.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170707%2Flarge%2F1499436070_1231.png&h=0aa07a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56928214&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56928214%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170708&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=9f0e2b24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56928214%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170708&h=1a0853c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56928214&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170708</a>"},{"pid":"7dcd4060ce406fdb5c4170188fe0b325e8915a3a","tid":312899,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"如果可以係91 同299 身上贏過大錢既真係高手中既高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}